From 6f20410d5ff9d30fc3806ff75d15b2ef37b875ca Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: "Ryan X. Charles" <ryan@ryanxcharles.com>
Date: Sat, 18 Jul 2026 13:29:39 -0500
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] Round all four corners of each split pane border
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Use a uniform continuous radius (window _cornerRadius, fallback 10)
on every corner of the pane stroke and R-w content/dim clip, including
internal T-junctions—not only window-outer corners.
---
 .../Splits/TerminalSplitTreeView.swift        | 33 ++-----------
 .../Ghostty/Surface View/InspectorView.swift  |  6 +--
 .../Ghostty/Surface View/SurfaceView.swift    | 49 ++++++-------------
 3 files changed, 22 insertions(+), 66 deletions(-)

